         "q": [
            "I HAVE A FREE ACCOUNT AND CANNOT ACCESS THE INTERNET FROM MY INSTANCES. WHY?"
         ],
         "a": "Our free account is to help new students learn the basics of information technology such as creating applications and connecting to them. To help students learn the core concepts of technology and its infrastructure. To make this possible without internet access from your instances we offer many different applications and operating systems. Try this tutorial to help get an understanding of how best to use the free account.\n\nAs you become more advanced, you may find you need internet access to learn more advanced concepts. You may sign up for a paid subscription which will provide internet access from your instances. As your understanding of technology increases, you may wish to have direct access to your websites and servers and may opt to subscribe to our advanced subscriptions.",
